### Products are fetched from Northwind **V2** and the consumption view
### renames the legacy PascalCase field names:
###   ProductID       → productId
###   ProductName     → productName
###   QuantityPerUnit → packSize
###   UnitPrice       → unitPrice
###   UnitsInStock    → inStock
###
### The client only ever sees the local names.
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Products?$top=5&$select=productId,productName,packSize,unitPrice,inStock

### $filter on a renamed field — translated to the remote name before the
### request goes out.
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Products?$filter=unitPrice gt 25&$orderby=unitPrice desc&$top=5

### $orderby on a renamed field
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Products?$orderby=productName&$top=3&$select=productId,productName
